intro_heading: What is National Day of Civic Hacking?
---
intro_body:

National Day of Civic Hacking is a nationwide day of action for volunteers around the country to put technology to work for the benefit of our local communities.
---
intro_body_2:

All outputs are open for everyone to use and re-use.
---
year_intro:

For National Day of Civic Hacking 2017, we want bring in more partners and provide more oppurtunities for people to pitch in. Here are some example events that you can host or attend around the country!
